<row>
<entry valign="top" align="left" namest="c1" nameend="c2"><emphasis effect="bold">Chapter Objectives:</emphasis>
<list id="fs-idm389247744" list-type="bulleted">
<item>Students will be able to explain the causes of the expansion of slavery and its influence on national politics and sectionalism.</item>
<item>Students will be able to evaluate national politics during the so-called Era of Good Feelings to determine if that title is valid.</item>
<item>Students will be able to analyze the effects of the Monroe Doctrine on domestic and international politics during this period.</item></list></entry>
</row>
